metadata.name: Landed
metadata.description:
Landed is an alternative dance record featuring afro rhythm, soulful vocals, jazzy piano and funky guitar. Like the cover art suggests, the song takes its time to go from a sensual start to rewarding climax. It offers a confident coming-of-age attitude towards aspirations, romances and worldliness.

See Tiehan's performance of Landed here: https://youtube.com/shorts/p8RrdZHl1N8?feature=share

Songwriting and Cover Art by Tiehan https://www.instagram.com/p/CsLo7ivpr9s/

Produced by Huang SiFu
